Basics is a minimalist social network designed to prioritize the privacy of the user and emphasize connection between individuals the user is close to or knows personally over group interactions with strangers from around the world. 

Social media has become somewhat problematic in recent years, with negative impacts ranging from detrimental effects on the mental health of young women to the rampant spread of misinformation and extremist ideologies that have resulted in violence and social unrest. This application aims to provide an alternative space for individuals to connect with each other without all of the complications of modern day social media, all while providing a modern platform that prioritizes the protection of user data and privacy. 
